  "text": "The values of leaf growth parameters and their susceptibility to environmental impacts vary with plant ontogeny [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . The phyllochron can change between genotypes in salak palm [CITATION_4] . In peach, the phyllochron can vary over the growing season [CITATION_5] and can differ within the same tree, relative to branch morphism and branch position [CITATION_6] .",
